  <brief_title>A Phase II Study of Maintenance With Azacitidine in MDS Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of Maintenance With Azacitidine in MDS Patients Achieving Complete or Partial Remission (CR or PR) After Intensive Chemotherapy</official_title>
